    <string name="peakflow_insight">PEAKFLOW INSIGHT</string>
    <string name="polarization_desc">"80/20 Model: 80% should be LOW intensity (Blue) and 20% HIGH intensity (Red). The 'Grey Zone' (Gray) is the middle ground that generates fatigue without maximum gains; avoid it in easy sessions."</string>
    <string name="metabolic_desc">"Fuel usage: Shows estimated glycogen (carbs) and fats burned based on intensity. Higher intensity relies more on glycogen, requiring longer recovery."</string>
    <string name="grey_zone_recommendation">"You are spending %1$s%% of your time in the 'Grey Zone'. Consider making your easy sessions easier (Z2) and your hard sessions harder (Z4/Z5)."</string>
    <string name="hydration_recommendation">"Heat conditions detected. Based on your intensity, we recommend rehydrating with ~%1$sL of water with electrolytes."</string>
